    dc:description "Figure 2. Allium ekimianum (Koyuncu 7847 / Elazig). Plant (A, B), flower (C), flower longitudinal section (D), inner tepal (D 1, D 2), outer tepal (D 3, D 4), pistil (E), capsule (F), seed (G), leaf sheathing (H), leaf cross section (I). (Drawn by Guelnur Eksi)." ;
