<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.62.7796.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Allium sintenisii (Koyuncu 9692 / Kahramanmaras). Plant (A 1, A 2), flower (B), flower longitudinal section (C), inner tepal (C 1, C 2), outer tepal (C 3, C 4), pistil (D), capsule (E), seed (F), bulblet (G), leaf sheathing (H), leaf surface (I). (Drawn by Guelnur Eksi)." ;
